      • beforeLogin

        public void beforeLogin(android.webkit.WebView webView,
               LoginRequestType requestType,
               GSObject params)
        Invoked before the web bridge begins a login process.
        Parameters:
        webView - The attached web view that initiated the login.
        requestType - A LoginRequestType value specifying the login endpoing - either "login", "addConnection" or "socialLogin" (for accounts namespace).
        params - The login request parameters.

      • onLoginResponse

        public void onLoginResponse(android.webkit.WebView webView,
                   GSResponse response)
        Invoked after the login process is finished.
        Parameters:
        webView - The attached web view that initiated the login.
        response - A response object with the login result.

      • onPluginEvent

        public abstract void onPluginEvent(android.webkit.WebView webView,
                 GSObject event,
                 java.lang.String containerID)
        Invoked when a Gigya JavaScript SDK plugin fires a custom event inside the web view (For example - commentUI's commentSubmitted).
        Parameters:
        webView - The attached web view that contains the origin plugin.
        event - The event object.
        containerID - The ID of the HTML element that contains the plugin.
